#: ../../T/trap-door.rst:17
msgid ""
"[techspeak] A trap-door function is one which is easy to compute but very "
"difficult to compute the inverse of. Such functions are :ref:`Good-Thing`\\s"
" with important applications in cryptography, specifically in the "
"construction of public-key cryptosystems."
msgstr ""
"[techspeak]trap-door関数とは、計算するのは容易だが、その逆を計算するのは非常に難しい関数である。そうした関数は\\ "
":ref:`Good-Thing`\\ で、暗号、特に公開鍵暗号系の構築に重要な応用を持つ。"
